## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="e3b4a-320">`WriteEvent`方法提供多載的字串與整數引數的組合。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e3b4a-320">The `WriteEvent` method provides overloads with combinations of string and integer arguments.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e3b4a-321">如果沒有任何這些組合相符的參數呼叫時，編譯器會使用<xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEvent%28System.Int32%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29?displayProperty=nameWithType>多載，這是比其他多載慢上許多。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e3b4a-321">If none of these combinations match the parameters for the call, the compiler uses the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEvent%28System.Int32%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29?displayProperty=nameWithType> overload, which is considerably slower than the other overloads.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e3b4a-322">請參閱詳細資料的多載頁面。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e3b4a-322">See the overload page for details.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e3b4a-323">在所有情況下，`eventid`參數應該是大於 0 或小於 65535，或在作業中，可能會發生錯誤。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e3b4a-323">In all cases, the `eventid` parameter should be greater than 0 or less than 65535 or errors can occur in the operation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e3b4a-324">如果發生錯誤，您可以取得錯誤來源的詳細資訊，藉由檢查輸出資料流的偵錯工具中，如果您有偵錯工具附加至處理程序引發的事件即可。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e3b4a-324">If errors do occur, you can get more information about the source of the error by checking the output stream of the debugger, if you have a debugger attached to the process firing events.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e3b4a-325">如果您有在發生錯誤的事件來源的 ETW 接聽程式，您也可以尋找 ETW 事件資料流中報告錯誤。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e3b4a-325">You can also look for errors reported in the ETW event stream, if you have an ETW listener on the event source where the error occurs.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e3b4a-326">當您實作的方法，便會被視為中的 ETW 事件<xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource>-衍生的類別。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e3b4a-326">When you implement a method that is identified as an ETW event in an <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource>-derived class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e3b4a-327">您必須呼叫基底類別<xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEvent%2A>方法並傳遞<xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventAttribute.EventId%2A>和實作的方法類似於下列範例中相同引數。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e3b4a-327">You must call the base class <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEvent%2A> method passing the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventAttribute.EventId%2A> and the same arguments as the implemented method similar to the following example.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
[Event(2, Level = EventLevel.Informational)]  
public void Info1(string arg1)  
{  
 base.WriteEvent(2, arg1);  
}  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e3b4a-328">您也可以建立自訂的多載使用<xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEventCore%2A>方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e3b4a-328">You can also create a custom overload by using the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEventCore%2A> method.</span></span>

  
  
